Package ch.ethz.vizzly.cache.memory

This package contains the implementation of a memory cache.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IndexedSignalData
    This class implements a data structure that holds measurements with time information that have been aggregated to a certain level of detail.
    IndexedSignalLocationData
    This class implements a data structure that holds measurements with time and location information that have been aggregated to a certain level of detail.
    MemCache
    This class implement a cache that stores all data in memory.
